-- GDP_DEFLATOR: DSD-completeness add (live-seed gap) — referenced by GDP_ANNUAL
-- obs dim_keys (15 rows, GE, year-on-year % change) but absent from the codelist,
-- which the V4 validate_observation_dim_key trigger rejected. Flat measure (no
-- parent), approach=growth as a metadata attribute (same shape as GDP_GROWTH),
-- unit_measure=PERCENT (V16 codelist), decimals=2. Label: GDP Deflator / მშპ-ის დეფლატორი.
